query:
DELETE FROM mailbox_emails WHERE
                               (account_id, email_id) IN (SELECT ?1, value->>'$[1]' FROM json_each(?2)) AND
                               (account_id, mailbox_id, email_id) NOT IN (
                                    SELECT ?1, value->>'$[0]', value->>'$[1]' FROM json_each(?2)
                                )
